				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10417843/three-thousand-to-one#post-4165341</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 25 Feb 2019 16:29:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Proasek</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2048131</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Ah yes, I was concerned about people picking up on that in a negative light. Each section is written slightly differently to reflect something in the character, and the third section is built around the detail oriented Thomas, with cramped sentences that each move through his reasoning. The other sections aren't intended to have this, however, so I'll probably try and take a pass at them to make the third part stand out more.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
