				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10417843#post-4165109</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10417843/three-thousand-to-one#post-4165109</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 25 Feb 2019 12:02:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Proasek</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2048131</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>First off, huge thanks to my primary critters, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2150500&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="LadyKatie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2150500)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" >LadyKatie</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-north" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4695462&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="Doctor North" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4695462)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-north" >Doctor North</a></span>, the latter of whom pinged me almost every day as I was writing this to make sure I was still working on it! Thanks to everyone else who's looked this over, including <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" >plaidypus</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpines" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2241229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="MrPines" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2241229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpines" >MrPines</a></span>, who went as far as to upvote this thing even before I posted it. Wowee.</p> <p>Thanks as well to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" >XilasCrowe</a></span>, who (after some badgering) donated their voice for the audio segment down at the bottom. I renamed a character after them in honor of it.</p> <p>And of course, how could I possibly forget to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" >djkaktus</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551096139" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" >Shaggydredlocks</a></span>, who contributed the two skips this work is based on. It literally could not exist without the work of these excellent lads.</p> <p>Think that's about it from me, I do so hope you enjoy DayBreaks, and let me know if you want to see more! Stay inside, kids!</p> 
				 	]]>
